## Term feed (VX) widget

The **Term feed (VX)** widget can be used to display taxonomy terms in Grid or Carousel view.

It utilizes a Card template that can be created in **WP AdminDesign ** **TaxonomiesPreview card**

Term feed allows you to display terms either by manual selection or by filtering them based on various criteria such as taxonomy, order etc.
